{"meta":{"title":"Portland Transporation System Plan","slug":"portland-transportation-system-plan","site":"http://pbot-tsp.surge.sh","date":"2017.05.20","description":"<p>Design &amp; Development of public policy &amp; GIS data presenting the City of Portlands plans for 20 years of public works development. The project has a back end that generates searchable, performant web content from canonical .docx files, as well as presenting an application for exploring GIS data.</p>\n","collection":"projects","timestamp":1495263600000},"content":"<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-FDz7Dm7/0/06d8752b/180x180/home-X5.png\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-FDz7Dm7/0/06d8752b/{width}x5000/home-X5.png\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"home\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>• Introduce project, public money and accountability, what for and why.\n• Key requirements around Section 508 and WCAAG AA, the Library computer.\n• Map / Text View etc.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-wtLbM6q/0/e06f6dea/180x180/txt-X4.png\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-wtLbM6q/0/e06f6dea/{width}x5000/txt-X4.png\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"txt\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>• Text only view, parsed to HTML from legal DocX files.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-JB6728d/0/44ff0340/180x180/index-XL.gif\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-JB6728d/0/44ff0340/{width}x5000/index-XL.gif\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"index\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Table of contents generated from the heading tags, accessible through the index. Scroll to animations keep the user from getting lost.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-6xkt8ZR/0/866a11d6/180x180/search-XL.gif\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-6xkt8ZR/0/866a11d6/{width}x5000/search-XL.gif\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"search\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>The complete text is searchable, allowing for quick location of  information by location or type.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-WDDb2MV/0/f418990b/180x180/layers-X5.png\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-WDDb2MV/0/f418990b/{width}x5000/layers-X5.png\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"layers\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Canonical data lives in the cities existing GIS, hosted and exposed via ArcGIS online and consumed by Leaflet.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-X4MQVL2/0/5ff57824/180x180/draw-X5.png\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-X4MQVL2/0/5ff57824/{width}x5000/draw-X5.png\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"draw\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Web-specific cartography and rendering support in leaflet …</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-z3tjSrh/0/5aa8532d/180x180/popup-X5.png\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-z3tjSrh/0/5aa8532d/{width}x5000/popup-X5.png\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"popup\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Exploration of features exposed via popup.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img\n          class=\"figure-image lazyload\"\n          src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-2ZnZVsk/0/a06a6e02/180x180/linking-XL.gif\"\n          data-optimumx=\"1.6\"\n          data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-2ZnZVsk/0/a06a6e02/{width}x5000/linking-XL.gif\"\n          data-sizes=\"auto\"\n          alt=\"linking\" />\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Connection between data in popups, connecting to relevant section in the text.</p>\n"}